text:
@BorisJohnson

author: Sam Hayes
text:
@BorisJohnson 
And with hospital appointments not running as usual, then there is more elderly that are being admitted in to these places as they can't afford 24hr care at home! My grandma is having to endure this for a third time! And as we are unable to vet these places out
